  "keyFeatures": [
    "16-color palette with retro game aesthetics inspired by PICO-8 and TIC-80",
    "Built-in Pyxel Editor for creating pixel art images, tilemaps, sounds, and music",
    "Cross-platform support: Windows, Mac, Linux, and Web (WebAssembly)",
    "4-channel audio with programmable sounds, music tracks, and MML support",
    "CLI tools for running, packaging, and converting apps to HTML/executable",
    "Keyboard, mouse, and gamepad input handling",
    "Image banks (3x 256x256), tilemaps (8x 256x256), and 64 definable sounds",
    "Perlin noise, math utilities, and collision detection built-in",
    "No-install web usage via Pyxel Code Maker and Web Launcher"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
